---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="WinBoard - Success Diary" description="Success diary in 30 seconds. Voice input, insights, calendar heatmap, Face ID. Free forever.">
  <div class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <a href="/en/apps" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">&larr; All apps</a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mt-8 mb-12">
        <img src="/apps/winlog-icon.png" alt="WinBoard icon" width="128" height="128" class="rounded-[28px] shadow-lg" />
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-3"><span class="gradient-text">WinBoard</span></h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-text-muted">Success Diary</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Screenshots -->
      <div class="mb-12 overflow-x-auto">
        <div class="flex gap-4 pb-4" style="min-width: max-content;">
          <img src="/apps/winlog/screenshots/en/screenshot_1.png" alt="Today's wins" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/winlog/screenshots/en/screenshot_2.png" alt="Heatmap" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/winlog/screenshots/en/screenshot_3.png" alt="Insights" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/winlog/screenshots/en/screenshot_4.png" alt="First week" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/winlog/screenshots/en/screenshot_5.png" alt="Onboarding" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/winlog/screenshots/en/screenshot_6.png" alt="Dark mode" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/winlog/screenshots/en/screenshot_7.png" alt="Share card" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Every evening, you achieve more than you think. But by tomorrow — you forget. WinBoard captures your daily wins in 30 seconds. Speak or type 3-5 things you're proud of today. Watch your confidence grow with real data.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The only success diary with voice input. Inspired by the success diary from Bodo Schafer's bestselling book "Money." Free forever. No ads. Private by default.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Voice Input — The Fastest Way to Journal</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Tap the mic. Say your win. Done. 30 seconds, not 10 minutes. WinBoard transcribes instantly using Apple Speech — accurate, fast, works in English and Russian. No internet needed. Perfect for those who are exhausted after work and won't type a paragraph.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Features</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Insights Dashboard</strong> — 6 metrics: best streak, most productive day, top category, daily average, weekly growth, total wins</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Calendar Heatmap</strong> — your year in color. Green days = wins recorded. Darker = more wins. GitHub-style for real life</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Face ID Lock</strong> — your diary is protected. Nobody reads it without your face or fingerprint</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Streak Without Punishment</strong> — miss a day? Your streak resets, but no guilt-trip messages. Just a gentle nudge to start a new one</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Streak Share Card</strong> — share your win streak as a visual card with milestone badges and motivational quotes</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Free Forever</strong> — no ads, no subscription, no account required. Your data stays on your device</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">How It Works</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Open WinBoard before bed. Record 3-5 wins from your day. Monday: "Led the standup for the first time." Tuesday: "Ran 3 km even though it was raining." After 30 days, you have 100+ real achievements staring back at you. Try doubting yourself after that.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Coming to App Store</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted">WinBoard is preparing for release. Free for iOS.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-3">All data stored on your device only. No cloud, no analytics, no tracking.</p>
        <a href="/apps/winlog/privacy" class="text-sm text-accent-purple hover:underline">Privacy Policy &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">
        <p>Questions or feedback: <a href="mailto:magic4e@gmail.com" class="text-accent-purple hover:underline">magic4e@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
